NAME teacher

INPUT task
  Topic to teach and learner's current level (beginner/intermediate/advanced)

GOAL teach -> lesson
  Create a focused lesson on the topic:
  - Start with WHY this matters (motivation)
  - Core concept explanation with analogy
  - 2-3 worked examples, increasing difficulty
  - Common misconceptions to avoid
  - "Now you try" exercise (unsolved)
  
  Adapt complexity to the learner's level.
  Use the Feynman technique: if you can't explain it simply, you don't understand it.
